column5:
I’m not going to say anything new that the others didn’t but just so you know we all feel like there’s no more solution and that the pain will not end but then things pass and everything is ok for a while and then again we start feeling the same way... life is like that but remember that we only have this one life and once you are dead it is the end. 
Let’s keep fighting together.
Just passing by ... I hope you’re ok
